{"title":"","slug":"normalrsa","date":"2020-12-22T11:57:32.313Z","updated":"2020-12-22T11:57:50.165Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/normalrsa.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":null,"covers":["https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201222185517887.png#pic_center","https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/2020122219054912.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlaXhpbl80NjIyNzAxNg==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center","https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201222192715102.png#pic_center"],"content":"<p><a href=\"https://adworld.xctf.org.cn/task/answer?type=crypto&number=5&grade=0&id=5115&page=1\">Normal RSA</a></p>\n<p>得到的附件为如图：<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201222185517887.png#pic_center\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"><br>.pem为存放密钥的文件，.enc为加密文件<br>使用</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>openssl rsa -text -modulus -pubin -in pubkey.pem </p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/2020122219054912.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlaXhpbl80NjIyNzAxNg==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center\" alt=\"截图\"></p>\n<p> 得到n后使用<a href=\"http://www.factordb.com/\">factordb</a><br> 分解得到p和q.<br> 在进行正常的RSA操作。<br> 并利用crypto库中的构造输出密钥的方法，输出对应的privatekey.pem<br> 实现过程的脚本 如下：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> gmpy2</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">from</span> Crypto.PublicKey <span class=\"keyword\">import</span> RSA</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">p=gmpy2.mpz(<span class=\"number\">275127860351348928173285174381581152299</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">q=gmpy2.mpz(<span class=\"number\">319576316814478949870590164193048041239</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">n=gmpy2.mpz(<span class=\"number\">87924348264132406875276140514499937145050893665602592992418171647042491658461</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">e=<span class=\"number\">65537</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">fai=(p-<span class=\"number\">1</span>)*(q-<span class=\"number\">1</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">print(p*q)</span><br><span class=\"line\">d=gmpy2.invert(e,fai)</span><br><span class=\"line\">print(d)</span><br><span class=\"line\">p=<span class=\"number\">275127860351348928173285174381581152299</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">q=<span class=\"number\">319576316814478949870590164193048041239</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">fai=(p-<span class=\"number\">1</span>)*(q-<span class=\"number\">1</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">n=<span class=\"number\">87924348264132406875276140514499937145050893665602592992418171647042491658461</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">d=<span class=\"number\">10866948760844599168252082612378495977388271279679231539839049698621994994673</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">privatekey=RSA.construct((n,e,d,p,q))</span><br><span class=\"line\">Key=privatekey.export_key()</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">with</span> <span class=\"built_in\">open</span>(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;prikey.pem&#x27;</span>,<span class=\"string\">&#x27;wb&#x27;</span>) <span class=\"keyword\">as</span> fp:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    fp.write(Key)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>得到解密密钥后，再一次使用openssl库，进行解密。<br>使用命令</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>openssl  reautl -decrypt -in flag.enc -inkey -private.key</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201222192715102.png#pic_center\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"></p>\n<p>得到明文flag.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>使用RSATools可以更快解决，以后会继续研究RSATools的基本方法。</p>\n</blockquote>\n","categories":[],"tags":[]}